LISTSERV Web Interface 2.4.1 2014-08-20T14:02:03Z JiscMail Helpline 2014-08-20T16:02:00+01:00 2014-08-20T16:02:00+01:00 Message regarding COUNSELLORS-NETWORK JiscMail List https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=COUNSELLORS-NETWORK;8eb1fb3f.1408 We require an existing subscriber(s) of this list to take over the running of the list.<br><br>The previous list owners cannot be contacted and so JiscMail are temporarily running this list until a new owner can be found.<br>If you would like to volunteer to help keep this list open and active, please contact us at helpline@jiscmail.ac.uk - we can provide training and support if needed.<br>If we don't have any volunteer then the list will be closed on Friday 5th September 2014.<br>When this happens subscribers will not be able to post messages to the list but archives will [...] JiscMail Helpline 2014-07-29T16:32:39+01:00 2014-07-29T16:32:39+01:00 New list owner required for COUNSELLORS-NETWORK JiscMail list https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=COUNSELLORS-NETWORK;1dd3b8fc.1407 JiscMail Helpline has recently tried to contact the list owners of this list, but the message we sent bounced.<br><br>In order for us to continue to provide this mailing list we require an existing subscriber(s) from a UK Educational/Research Organisation to volunteer to take over the running of the list. JiscMail Helpline is currently managing the list as a temporary measure, if you wish to volunteer to run this list - check that you meet the criteria for running a list: https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk/groups/startagroup/grouprequestform.html and if you do contact helpline@jiscmail.ac.uk as soon as you possibly can.
